text: Thaimí González (born 6 November 1995) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * contramaestre-present-in-the-pan-american-games Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
